19891013000000000_21	Although not as old as the origin of life the problem of keeping time has plagued humans for eons.	although old origin life problem keep time ha plagu human eon
19891013000000000_22	From the beginning of time until 1967 timekeeping methods were based on the rotation of the Earth.	begin time timekeep method base rotat earth
19891013000000000_23	In that year the world switched to a newer form of timekeeping based on the oscillations of cesium atoms in a so called atomic clock.	year world switch newer form timekeep base oscil cesium atom call atom clock
